Lach. has rightly seen that our reading implies the loss of one or more verses in which the poet passed from Venus to Memmius: he suggests animumque, aye, Memmi, which would complete the sentence in a. way: so would corque, inclute Memmi, or the like. 66 tollere. tendere Lamb. ed. 3 Lech. from Nonius ‘teste nostris antiquiore '.
